In [[Maztica]]'s [[Payit]] region, conch-shells used to craft battle [[horn]]s and horns to signal sacrificial processions. In a similar manner, the [[Waterdhavian Watch]] used conch horns to sound the alarms in the city harbors.

Some [[priest]]s of [[Umberlee]], namely [[Magat]] of [[Lathtarl's Lantern]], wore [[helmet]]s carved out of large conch shells, worth 15 [[gp]] undamaged.{{Cite dungeon/64/Grotto of the Queen|10}}

Aquatic species, like [[morkoth]], used large conch shells affixed to belts, as wearable pouches or containers.
